OL,6,FPaymaster General John Glen will today
OL,7,Fset out in Parliament how much people
OL,8,Faffected by the scandal will be paid
OL,9,Fin compensation.
OL,11,FMembers of the infected blood
OL,12,Fcommunity expect the government will
OL,13,Fsimplify payments into five main
OL,14,Fcategories: injury, social impact,
OL,15,Fautonomy, care and financial loss.
OL,17,FMinisters have earmarked around #10
OL,18,Fbillion for a compensation package.
