OL,6,FThe 2,527-page report from the
OL,7,Finquiry, published on Monday, found
OL,8,Fthe infected blood scandal "could
OL,9,Flargely have been avoided" and there
OL,10,Fwas a "pervasive" cover-up to hide the
OL,11,Ftruth.
OL,13,FMinisters failed to act in order to
OL,14,Fsave face and expense, the inquiry
OL,15,Fsaid, with the current government
OL,16,Fcriticised for failing to act
OL,17,Fimmediately on recommendations around
OL,18,Fcompensation which were made last year.
