OL,6,FInquiry Chair Sir Brian said: "What I
OL,7,Fhave found is that disaster was no
OL,8,Faccident.
OL,10,F"People put their trust in doctors and
OL,11,Fthe government to keep them safe and
OL,12,Fthat trust was betrayed.
OL,14,F"Then the government compounded that
OL,15,Fagony by telling them that nothing
OL,16,Fwrong had been done, that they'd had
OL,17,Fthe best available treatment and that
OL,18,Fas soon as tests were available they
OL,19,Fwere introduced and both of those
OL,20,Fstatements were untrue.
